* Background 

Fork of the project  (https://bitbucket.org/btosch/superchromeide) for
the Google Seattle HTML5 Web App Hackathon
(http://html5hack.appspot.com/preso/crhack.html).


This application includes several features for both HTML5 as well as
Google Chome Web Store.

** HTML5

- CSS3 transitions/transforms/drop shadow/border radius
http://www.alistapart.com/articles/understanding-css3-transitions/ 
- Web Fonts
- querySelector: classList and dataset
- CSS3 Flexbox (Flexible Box Layout )
http://www.w3.org/TR/css3-flexbox/
- Speech Input
- File APIs
- Web Sockets 
http://dev.w3.org/html5/websockets/
- XHR updates
- Data Views 
- Typed Arrays (not active)
http://www.khronos.org/registry/typedarray/specs/latest/

